README file for $FIRSTBASEHOME/applications/sample_src area.

This is an example of a simple C program using firstbase.

termtest
--------
a simple program that tests a few display and input functions.

rectest
-------
a simple program that allows adding/reading records
to a very simple database named `dbase'.

